headline: I Am Not Convinced The Seas Will Settle For Huntington Ingalls' Shipbuilding Business
summary: Huntington Ingalls struggles with margin pressures from fixed contracts and budget reliance, limiting upside despite recovery. Learn why HII stock is a hold.
